texts.text: It's time.
>After a night has passed, the hour of the execution draws near...
>You are again in the same hall as the previous day,
>being held down by demons.
Guess who's here to see you? Let them in!
>The heavy doors open at the boss' bidding.
>Behind the doors stand the Dx2s of Yotsuya city and the prisoners you rescued yesterday.
Lucky for you they didn't abandon you.
Glare at the demon.
Look at the people of Yotsuya city.
What? I was paying you a compliment.
Hey, no one's hurt. That's what matters right?
Anyway, thank you all for coming here.
If you would kindly hand us your weapons please?
Alright everybody, do as it says.
>The Dx2s of Yotsuya city all throw down their weapons and smartphones.
Without them, we won't be much help to you in your war against other demons though.
>The Dx2s hold their hands up as a sign of resignation.
Don't worry, you'll get them back.
I see...
You complied to our demands, so I'm going to let this one go free.
The hostages seem to be all here boss.
Good, let's make the exchange then.
...Let's go guys.
>The hostages start moving forward...
Shouldn't have run from the start.
>Just as they are about to
>reach where you are...
Now!
Chaaaaarge!
>The unarmed hostages make their move!
Help me rescue the prisoner first!
Got it!
You can count on me!
>The people of Yotsuya begin to fight the demons with their bare hands!
>The demons holding you down leave you to engage them.
>You are free to move!
You're free! Can you move?
C'mon! This way!
Take that...! Eeeek!
I ain't done yet...! Arrrgh!
>The screams of the people ring out behind you...
Look back.
Keep running.
Don't look back! There's nothing you can do without your weapons!
Just follow me!
Smartphones out everybody! Time to fight!
>The Dx2s take out their smartphones and start to summon demons!
Heh, just as I thought. The ones you tossed were fakes.
They're called counterfeits asshole!
We gathered them from shops just in case something like this happens!
You sly sons of bitches...
Deploy all your demons! And hand everyone a weapon!
>The people are handed weapons by the demons summoned by the Dx2s,
>and one by one they rejoin the fight.
Why do this?
Why didn't you escape?
You reminded us what its like to act on a whim.
Besides, you never ran away when you
helped Akito and saved the people of Yotsuya.
So in a way we're just imitating you.
You did the same for us.
You could've gone your own way and left us to our own problems, but you didn't.
In a world like this, that means something.
So we're just returning the favor.
We became Downloaders to fight demons, and now's the time for us to
make a stand and get rid of them once and for all.
But right now you need to get somewhere safe! We'll find your weapons for you!
That ain't happening, humans!
>Suddenly you find yourselves surrounded by demons...
>One of them raises its sword and swings...!
No... you don't!
Get out of here! Me and dad will hold them back for yo-
U-Ughhh!
Ryo!
>Ryo's body is pierced by a giant sword...

*Groan*
I... Just couldn't take it anymore...
Don't try to talk Ryo!
They killed mom and...
I-I wanted to avenge her...!
It's okay Ryo! Don't...
The others... Wanted the same...
That's why we didn't want to run...!
Even though we couldn't fight like the Downloaders... We...
Ryo? Stay with me Ryo! Ryo!
>People are being killed left and right
>trying to shield you from harm...
>Your soundless cry of anguish rings across the battlefield...
Why...
Weapons... Power...
Get a hold of yourself! Remember why we're doing this!
If these mean so much to you, don't ever lose them again!
[sys user_name]!
>Pixie descends right into the circle of demons surrounding you!
Pixie...
You're alive...
I went through a lot of shit because of you! Are you gonna make it up to me or what?
Of course I am! There's no way in hell I was gonna die like that!
But now's not the time. Take these!
>Pixie gives you your smartphone and Armament back.
Go get 'em!
Devil Download!
You're all going down!
>The final battle against the demons begins...
You're hard to kill, I'll give you that...!
So you're not the average everyday Downloader. I thought as much.
But look around you.
>The Dx2s and the demons are killing each other like crazy.
>Dead bodies are all over the place...
Was your rebellion worth it?
Is this what you wanted?
No! You wanted them to live!
But by giving them false hope, you killed them!
When all I was trying to do was protect them with my reign!
Just shut up already!
Glare.

Alright, whatever...
A fool to the end...
If you want to fight me so much, I'll dispose of you myself!
